reviewText: Yogi Bear has the best 3D effects of any movie we have purchased so far. The grandkids love it!

Loaded with great 3D gimmicks especially Yogi Bear, it's a fun kids story but lots of fun to watch and the Guardians movie is a visual spectacular.  This set is a very good value for your money, all the better if you have children or grand kids at home.
Much better than expected.  Guardians and Yogi Bear have great 3D effects so they definitely make the purchase worth it.  Happy Feet 2 is good but not much different from 2d.

Loved the movies. However, Guardians and Happy Feet disc labels were in a foreign language. I panicked at first thinking the movies not in English, but when I inserted the disc, they were in English. Only the labels in another language. Might be copies.
Video's were packaged well.  Three good movies
Great fun for the whole family.
